data.description: Bring ALL the Animals to this GORGEOUS Mini FARM! Welcome to The Rock, GA.  True Ranch Home on 3.3 secluded ACRES. THREE covered Animal-friend Enclosures, and TWO Large cross-fenced Grazing pastures! Fully updated 3 bedroom, and 2 bath home with with an Open Floorplan, and ALL the Charm. At the back of the property line you'll find Potato Creek to enjoy to your heart's desire. A Red storage barn, and Detached 2-car Garage/ Workshop with connecting Breezeway makes this the home the has it all! Granite countertops and fully updated.... NOW is your CHANCE to have the perfect amount of property with LOW maintenance. Welcome Home... to 1081 PIEDMONT ROAD! Open House this Saturday 11/27 from 1-4pm
